# Cursor Rules for Smart Blog Platform with AI Content Suggestions

## Project Context
This is an AI-powered blogging platform built with Node.js and Express.js. The project implements NLP algorithms for content analysis, title generation, and SEO optimization.

## Tech Stack
- **Backend**: Node.js 18+, Express.js 4.18+
- **Database**: MongoDB with Mongoose ODM
- **AI/ML**: Custom NLP algorithms, optional OpenAI integration
- **Package Manager**: npm

## Code Style & Conventions
- Use ES6+ JavaScript features
- Follow async/await pattern
- Use camelCase for variables and functions
- Use descriptive names for AI functions
- Add comments for NLP algorithms
- Keep text processing functions modular

## File Structure
```
/
├── server.js
├── routes/
│   ├── posts.js
│   └── ai.js
├── services/
│   ├── titleGenerator.js
│   ├── contentAnalyzer.js
│   ├── keywordExtractor.js
│   └── outlineGenerator.js
├── models/
│   └── Post.js
└── utils/
