```

## AI/ML Development Guidelines
- Implement NLP algorithms in separate service files
- Document text processing logic clearly
- Handle edge cases: empty input, special characters
- Optimize for performance (cache common operations)
- Test with various content types
- Consider multi-language support (future)

## API Development
- Follow RESTful conventions
- Use consistent response formats
- Implement proper error handling
- Add input validation for text inputs
- Rate limit AI endpoints to prevent abuse
- Document API endpoints clearly

## Text Processing Best Practices
- Normalize text input (trim, lowercase where needed)
- Handle special characters and encoding
- Implement text sanitization
- Use efficient string operations
- Cache processed results when possible

## Security Best Practices
- Validate and sanitize all text inputs
- Implement rate limiting on AI endpoints
- Protect API keys and secrets
- Prevent injection attacks
- Content moderation for user-generated content

## Performance Optimization
- Cache topic suggestions
- Optimize text processing algorithms
- Use async processing for heavy operations
- Implement pagination for large datasets
- Monitor API response times

